# दोष and stuck terms — the two faces of failure. No exceptions: a failure is
# either an error *value* you can inspect, or a term that simply stops reducing.
# Run: sutra run examples/dosha.sutra

प्रयोग शीर्ष([])।          # head of empty list ⇒ दोष("रिक्ता सूची")
प्रयोग शीर्ष([9, 8])।      # ⇒ 9
प्रयोग 5 / 0।              # ⇒ दोष("शून्येन भागः …")  (errors are data)
प्रयोग शीर्ष(5)।           # no rule applies ⇒ the term stays stuck: शीर्ष(5)
